    "description": "Singularity Runner is a simple casual game that relies on your reflexes. <br><br>The player-controlled hero runs forward automatically, and the player can control his running path. <br><br>When a hero changes course, the player scores points, but he cannot touch enemies unless he is in possession of a sword or shield. <br><br>The shield will protect the player from death, but it will disappear after hitting the enemy and interrupt the combo score. <br><br>The sword also disappears after hitting an enemy, but additionally it defeats him and does not interrupt the combo score. <br><br>When a player enters an opponent without a sword or shield, the game ends and the points scored are saved in the ranking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2> <br>You can play campaign or arcade.<br>Campaign has 6 levels to finish.<br>There are three arcade game modes: Endless Game, Time Limit and Time Attack. <br>Each mode has a separate ranking.<br><br>Run to victory, avoid or defeat your opponents, catch animals - helpers, collect useful items and much more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Control</h2> Left click to change the player's path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achivements:</h2> Lots of achievements to unlock!",
